Package: OptReSample
Type: Package
Title: Computing Optimal Adaptive Designs
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Maximilian Pilz
Maintainer: Maximilian Pilz <pilz@imbi.uni-heidelberg.de>
Description: OptReSample provides the computation of optimal adaptive two stage designs for a Gaussian distributed outcome. 
	The designs are optimal w.r.t. the expected sample size under a point alternative hypothesis. 
